{
  "texts": [
    "Several investigations have been carried out that focus on systematic reviews of the topic.",
    "For example, Perera and Lankathilaka (2023) examined both benefits and drawbacks.",
    "On the other hand, Imran and Almusharraf (2023) analyzed the related opportunities and challenges.",
    "Additionally, Vargas-Murillo, de la Asunción, and de Jesús Guevara-Soto (2023) investigated the topic's impact, benefits, and use.",
    "However, none of the analyzed articles have addressed crucial aspects such as validity, usefulness, and time optimization in applying ChatGPT in higher education."
  ]
}